BranchNbound_RegretSlabbedPenalty - Class in mas.localSchedulingproxy.algorithm
Minimizes penalty of a given sequence of jobs by using branch and bound algorithm To use it, create a node with state equal to ArrayList of a sequence of jobs The solution for the given job sequence will be calculated and stored in the ArrayList "best" Minimum penalty will be given by the variables "lowBound".
BranchNbound_RegretSlabbedPenalty(ArrayList<Batch>) - Constructor for class mas.localSchedulingproxy.algorithm.BranchNbound_RegretSlabbedPenalty
